NK036(chi)026:1: // 'khrul zhig seng ge rgyab pa'i rnam thar bzhugs /
NK036(chi)026:3: e ma ngo mtshar chos nyid theg dgu'i mkha' la
NK036(chi)026:4: thugs rje'i skal ldan pho mo la nyi 'od shar
NK036(chi)026:5: // rjes 'jug gi ma rig ling thog skye med mkha' la yal //
NK036(chi)026:6: kun la 'dzin med sprol bral chos kyi dbyings su mnyam nyid ro gcig pa'i //
NK036(chi)026:7: re sa 'gro mgon drin can bla ma rnams la gus pas phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK036(chi)026:8: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs +aahmh'u /
NK036(chi)026:9: 'khrul zhig rjes 'jug gi don du me long rdo rjes zhus pa /
NK036(chi)026:10: bla ma'i lo rgyus zur tsam ni //
NK036(chi)026:11: yul la khyad 'phags g.yu ru grwa yi nang //
NK036(chi)026:12: yab shangs pa'i rnal 'byor pa bzang po yin skad /
NK036(chi)026:13: yum bkra shis dngos grub gnyis kyi sras //
NK036(chi)026:14: yum so ba 'brang du sku 'khrungs ngo mtshar rtags
NK036(chi)026:15: nyi ma shar ba dang ri rtse la phyin pa
NK036(chi)026:18: skye ba sngon du chos kyi 'brel bas las 'phro sad //
NK036(chi)026:19: pas 'dir bla ma bzang po'i dpon por 'khrungs /
NK036(chi)026:20: lo dgu'i bla ma kun la /
NK036(chi)026:21: dus su gsal 'debs mos gus bskyangs //
NK036(chi)026:23: lo bcu lon nas nges 'byung dad pa skyes //
NK036(chi)026:25: 'jig rten tshe 'di dag la 'i phyogs su gtong re dbu snyung ba zhes blo ma zhugs //
NK036(chi)026:26: thams cad byams pa 'jig pa'i chos can mig cer re mi bden rdzun //
NK036(chi)026:27: sgyu ma lta bur sangs rgyas kyis mdo rgyud rnams su /
NK036(chi)026:29: ma gtogs pa 'di rnams bden bden rtag rtag 'dra ba 'di lta bu //
NK036(chi)026:30: 'khor ba 'di la sems shing 'jigs pas shum shum sku lus kyi spu zing zing byas //
NK036(chi)026:31: bcu gnyis lon dus mi la gus pa'i bza' bca'
NK036(chi)026:32: la mtho 'grogs byas pa gzhan gyi spyod pa la
NK036(chi)026:33: // thugs mug skyo ba drag po yul mi skyes pa de rnams gting nas skyes //
NK036(chi)026:34: dus de na mtho 'grogs khyad gsod mi byed dam bca' mdzad //
NK036(chi)026:36: bcu gsum lon tshe mtshan mnal lam chu mig gtsang ma rdol ba dang /
NK036(chi)026:37: nyi ma shar ba zla ba shar ba sogs ltas bzang po byung ltas lung bstan ni //
NK036(chi)026:38: thugs rje chen pos mdzad cing rdzogs de'i dus su chen gtad //
NK036(chi)026:39: spyan ras gzigs kyis byin brlabs thubs rje des //
NK036(chi)026:40: ngan zhing mi gang dbul zhing sprang po dang ngan long rnams la shig dang lji ba la //
NK036(chi)026:41: snying rje ma bzod dus rgyun du /
NK036(chi)026:44: bco brgyad lon tshe bden 'khor 'das snang srid kyis bsdus snang ba thams cad med khong du tshud //
NK036(chi)026:46: gtad med smyon pa'i spyod brang dang barla dang tshang
NK036(chi)026:47: ra la khyad med par rtogs pa'i sgo nas skabs
NK036(chi)026:49: pas yang dus gcig gi tshe a ma na re
NK036(chi)026:50: khyod kyis gsol mchod gyis zer nas zan g.yag gtad
NK036(chi)026:51: pa rgyal po mchod bsen mo mchod byas pas khyod
NK036(chi)026:54: sems kyis sems bltas dngos med chos thams cad /
NK036(chi)026:58: bral snying po'i don de khong du chud //
NK036(chi)026:60: dgung lo nyi shu rtsa lnga zer /
NK036(chi)026:61: lon nas tshe 'dir bya ba blos btang nas /
NK036(chi)026:64: dang bkra shis sgang pa ste mkhan slob gnyis po /
NK036(chi)026:66: mkhan bdag gi slob mdzad de thub pa'i bstan pa /
NK036(chi)026:69: dam chos pa'i 'dul ba'i bsrung bya dang bslab bya'i don /
NK036(chi)026:72: de nas bla ma'i drin can spyan sngar byon te seng ge rgyab tu /
NK036(chi)026:75: gting phyung dbang nas khrid ste zhang mtshal pa'i chos skor /
NK036(chi)026:77: yul de nas zhing btsong nas 'khor gsum dag par byas //
NK036(chi)026:78: mkhan slob nyi zla zung gcig ts+aa ri ba //
NK036(chi)026:83: ras pa dri ras chung pa'i a thung /
NK036(chi)026:84: med zhi byed spyod skabs dang po dang /
NK036(chi)026:86: 'pho ba spyi rtol ma gser srang ma /
NK036(chi)026:87: dam pa'i sgrub pa dang po lugs /
NK036(chi)026:89: sprul sku gzhan 'bum ston phyar byung gtum mo gsang sgrub bde mchog nam mkha' dang mnyam pa dang /
NK036(chi)026:91: mkhas btsun khyad 'phags slob dpon jo sras rnams //
NK036(chi)026:93: myur zab gdams pa'i gnad zhus bla ma brgyad //
NK036(chi)026:94: khyad 'phags chos bdag gu ru jo 'ber gyi thugs kyis bzung nas /
NK036(chi)026:95: gu ru gtsug gi rgyan gcig po //
NK036(chi)026:96: dbang rdzogs rdzogs pa chen po snying tig yongs su /
NK036(chi)026:97: man ngag dpe rgyud rjes gnang bcas //
NK036(chi)026:100: ba snying tig rgyal ba'i dgos pa ste //
NK036(chi)026:101: yid spyod tshul ji ltar gsungs na /
NK036(chi)026:102: tshig la ma brten mngon sum du //
NK036(chi)026:103: mtha' bral nam mkha'i mthong nas 'od zer 'phros //
NK036(chi)026:104: zhi khro rang gsal bstan pa'i drin can lags //
NK036(chi)026:105: mi 'di'i lar ni che dag spangs te dman sa bzung //
NK036(chi)026:106: rgyun du sgrub pa mchog gi lhur dus rgyun du
NK036(chi)026:107: blangs ri khrod dben sa zhang gi bzhugs gnas khro
NK036(chi)026:109: che 'brel tshe 'di las sangs rgya chung 'brel snying
NK036(chi)026:110: po'i thabs rdugs kyang sprul sku'i zhing don dang sprad
NK036(chi)026:112: med do rjes 'jug bu slob rnams go ba longs //
NK036(chi)026:113: dus ngan sems can la skyo shas yi tshe 'di pa rnams mug lam khyer zhing khams blta //
NK036(chi)026:114: snang ba mi bstun thig le 'di la goms pa su byed nga dang gcig /
NK036(chi)026:115: sangs rgyas dus gsum gyi yon tan thams cad kyang
NK036(chi)026:116: rdzogs te a ti'i sku gdung 'bar ba nas gsungs
NK036(chi)026:117: pa bzhin chos zad ka dag tu /
NK036(chi)026:120: kye ma 'khrul zhig drin can sangs rgyas dbon po kye //
NK036(chi)026:121: dred po gnod pa'i gdung shugs 'o dus rgyun du /
NK036(chi)026:123: brgyud pa'i bla ma'i bla ma drin can 'khrul zhig rin po che //
NK036(chi)026:124: mi lus snying po'i don can gong ma la ltos nas /
NK036(chi)026:126: 'bral med bla ma dang thugs rje'i thag pa rgyun dus du thongs //
NK036(chi)026:127: theg chen zhing sngags gsar rnying gnyis ka la nyams len thengs pa byung //
NK036(chi)026:129: gus byas so byin rlabs chu rgyun phobs //
NK036(chi)026:130: snying le lo can med po yis nyams len phyi zla ba phyi ma dang sang phod du /
NK036(chi)026:133: rtogs glo bur rkyen ci la yang brten nas gtad med du /
NK036(chi)026:134: ston cig rtsa ba bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro gsum //
NK036(chi)026:135: 'khrul zhig seng ge rgya ba'i rnam thar rdzogs so //
NK036(chi)026:137: grub thob me long rdo rje'i rnam thar bzhugs /
NK036(chi)026:138: +aahmh'u sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi snying po /
NK036(chi)026:140: sna rnam rdo rje bdud 'joms byon //
NK036(chi)026:141: da dung skye ba 'ga' zhig brgyud //
NK036(chi)026:142: 'gro don mi byed sbas tshul byed //
NK036(chi)026:143: lan gcig skye ba lnga brgya'i dus //
NK036(chi)026:144: chos nyid mngon du gyur pa yis //
NK036(chi)026:145: klong rdol mi yi seng ge ni //
NK036(chi)026:146: me long ming tu btags pa 'byung //
NK036(chi)026:147: de rjes o rgyan yul du mchi //
NK036(chi)026:149: zhes o rgyan gyi lung byang chen mo nas gsungs so //
NK036(chi)026:150: +aahmh'u h+r+aihsangasa rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi phrin las /
NK036(chi)026:151: ma ni pad+me h'u h+r+aihyi dam gyi snying po /
NK036(chi)026:153: bde gshegs chos kyi dbyings mchog kun gyi gi nor bu dgos 'dod thams cad 'byung bas /
NK036(chi)026:156: drug sems can skyabs gnas dri med nyi zla lta bu'i sku //
NK036(chi)026:158: sel byed sman gdams ngag mchog bdud zab mo rtsi mos gus can la ster mdzad pa'i //
NK036(chi)026:160: can bla ma rnams ma lus la /
NK036(chi)026:166: 'jug ngang nas dgos 'dod ci bsam pa /
NK036(chi)026:168: zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhi yis phrin las 'gro ba gdul dka' ba /
NK036(chi)026:170: smin dbang grol bskyed rdzogs byin rlabs chen pos gzhan snang chos la bsgyur mdzad pa'i //
NK036(chi)026:171: yid ma mkha' 'gro'i sngags gsang kyi lha /
NK036(chi)026:172: tshogs ma lus la gus yid pas sku gsung thugs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK036(chi)026:173: gting zab pa gsal ye shes chen po'i rig pa 'od po che //
NK036(chi)026:175: shar dri med dag gi mdangs ldan sna lnga rigs lnga yab yum sku /
NK036(chi)026:177: byar med lhun gyis grub pa /
NK036(chi)026:179: nyid ngang du 'khor 'das ka dag pa'i //
NK036(chi)026:180: sems rang sems nyid kun tu bzang la gus pas phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK036(chi)026:181: kye bdag gus dad me long la /
NK036(chi)026:183: snying gi bu rnams spro phyir du //
NK036(chi)026:184: rnam par gsal byed rdzun bden po bshad kyang /
NK036(chi)026:185: gyi me long bri chos pa'i don du /
NK036(chi)026:187: mnyam sprang smyon zla ba mun sel /
NK036(chi)026:188: med sbas pa'i rnal 'byor thugs kyi sprul pa ni //
NK036(chi)026:189: sa gtsang ri mtho sgrags nang 'gro mgon gdan sa ru //
NK036(chi)026:190: zhang rin po che'i dar phug ma 'bar 'khrul yum gyi lto na yod tsam na /
NK036(chi)026:191: rmi ltas bzang po dpag tu med gsungs /
NK036(chi)026:195: chung ngu'i dus na lo gnyis nas gtor ma gtong /
NK036(chi)026:196: dge rtags dkar gsol 'debs phyag dang chos spyod /
NK036(chi)026:199: sbyangs sgrib g.yogs chung bas mngon shes phra 'di 'ong bya ba dang mo dang //
NK036(chi)026:200: chu shul zla ba mun sel /
NK036(chi)026:201: sprang po'i rgyu mtshan dus de nyid nas gsal //
NK036(chi)026:203: du bsod nams bsog pa'i 'jur gegs kha nas phris /
NK036(chi)026:204: byas pa'i zla gcig phyir bsrings pa'i rnam smin gyis //
NK036(chi)026:205: skye dman ma yis btub tshad 'khor chung bas /
NK036(chi)026:207: mi sgo 'grigs pas rgya gad shig gi ser ba babs //
NK036(chi)026:209: dwa phrug bshes med par nyung ma dang thal ba kur bas rtsa gnyid log tu song ba dang /
NK036(chi)026:210: than chen chos pas ma myong dgu gcig myong dkor
NK036(chi)026:211: chas med par nas bre gsum gyis zla ba gcig
NK036(chi)026:212: thub par byas / de dus 'chi ba dran nas
NK036(chi)026:213: gsol ba mang po btab ste kha la nyin mtshan
NK036(chi)026:214: thub par byas / med par ngus // grub thob mched gnyis /
NK036(chi)026:215: za lung drin can gcig yin zhi byed lam gsum
NK036(chi)026:216: phag mo ra lugs in+d+ra b+hu ti'i thabs lam dam
NK036(chi)026:217: pa 'phyar chung gi gsang sgrub phag nag bka' ma
NK036(chi)026:218: zhus / pa dang mkhan chen se lung pas //
NK036(chi)026:220: dus su btsun zhang po sgom chen pa gcig gis khrid nas /
NK036(chi)026:221: chung byas te 'dul khrims lo bcu bdun tshun chad /
NK036(chi)026:223: de dus dbyar dgun lnga tsam /
NK036(chi)026:224: zangs mtshor sgom lo byas pa'i tshe //
NK036(chi)026:225: 'dre rtog cho 'phrul chen ban d+he gcig gis dngos su chir chir mnan /
NK036(chi)026:226: bo byung ba'i lo rgyus dang //
NK036(chi)026:228: stong sems par rtogs pas lus po 'di med na gcig tu 'dug pa snyam nas /
NK036(chi)026:230: dbyangs nyams blangs mched grogs kun gyis kha dus la ma babs zer /
NK036(chi)026:232: bco lnga lon pa'i dus su seng ge rgyab grub
NK036(chi)026:233: thob zwa lung pa'i zhal nas khyod rang gi bla
NK036(chi)026:234: ma ban rgan yin pas bgres yod par 'dug song
NK036(chi)026:236: brtse bas thugs kyis bzung nas gtsug gi rgyan 'bral med gcig mdzad //
NK036(chi)026:237: zla bzhi gzim khang bla yer 'bral zla ba gnyis snyun /
NK036(chi)026:238: med brten nas zla drug lon tshe gshegs //
NK036(chi)026:239: lug zla'i tshes bcu bzhi la /
NK036(chi)026:241: mos gus rmi lam du chos mang po gsungs bslab bya mang po mdzad o rgyan na yod gsung /
NK036(chi)026:242: thob pas rten rnams lag tu byon //
NK036(chi)026:243: bcu drug lon tshe zhogs rgan mo thugs rje zer ba gcig gis byas pas gnyis ka 'tshengs /
NK036(chi)026:246: bka' yi don mtha' bral stong pa /
NK036(chi)026:247: rig rang sems nam mkha' lta bur rtogs //
NK036(chi)026:248: dran snang yid la dran pa la lhag ma bzhag par /
NK036(chi)026:249: dbyangs su blangs shing smyon pa'i spyod pa byas //
NK036(chi)026:250: stag sgo mkhar chu ri brag gnyan khrod dben sa brten //
NK036(chi)026:251: chu 'thung rde'u 'bru chen bdud rtsi'i bcud len lo mang po /
NK036(chi)026:253: nas bre gang gis g.yu brag dang dung lung du /
NK036(chi)026:254: zla gcig nyi shu thub par byas lo nyi shu rtsa lnga phan chad la /
NK036(chi)026:255: khyi lpags gdan re ras rkyang re la brten pa dang //
NK036(chi)026:256: dka' nga ma shi'i bar du nas khal gnyis las
NK036(chi)026:257: mang ba tshag mi byed pa dang mtshams dang them
NK036(chi)026:258: spangs dang 'dag char dang smra bcad byas nas sgrub
NK036(chi)026:260: spyad sdug sran bskyed nas chos kyi phyogs su 'bungs //
NK036(chi)026:261: bco brgyad lon tshe 'gran med sangs rgyas dpon po rgyal mtshan /
NK036(chi)026:263: rdzogs chen snying thig ngo sprad chos nyid mngon sum bstan //
NK036(chi)026:266: tsam la ma brten sku gsum rjen par mthong //
NK036(chi)026:267: rdo rje sems dpa' dngos su mthong /
NK036(chi)026:268: mthong lo tsam du go bar ma shor ma gyur snang srid dbyings rnam par dag pa'o //
NK036(chi)026:270: de 'dzin zhen pa med stong par rtogs pas 'khor 'das brjod tshig gi gzhi bral //
NK036(chi)026:271: rdzogs chen brgyud pa rnams dang rmi lam nang du mjal //
NK036(chi)026:272: gdung shugs dga' ba'i sems kyis brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs byas //
NK036(chi)026:273: rtsa gsum lon tshe gung thang dar chud dar phug tu /
NK036(chi)026:274: mnyam med sangs rgyas ras pa la //
NK036(chi)026:275: rdo rje phag mo la sogs gter chos ma lus pa //
NK036(chi)026:277: 'khrul gcod bka' rgya ma dang gdams ngag dpag med zhus //
NK036(chi)026:278: dgos 'dod chos kyi gter rnyed 'phongs pa'i dbul ba bsal gzhan la tshom ma dgos /
NK036(chi)026:279: dbyar dgun gsum tsam brten nas bla ma dgung la gshegs //
NK036(chi)026:281: 'bral med snying rmi lam du mjal nas chos mang po gsungs phag mo klu 'dul gyi lung gnang /
NK036(chi)026:282: phyis kyang mjal ba yin gsungs /
NK036(chi)026:283: la bcangs pa'i byin rlabs rgyun chad med //
NK036(chi)026:284: rtsa bzhi lon tshe ye shes phag mo nyid dang
NK036(chi)026:285: mjal ka ba can du sbyin sreg byas pas brag
NK036(chi)026:288: zog po'i rdzun rkyal rdzun yin zer te rdzun la
NK036(chi)026:289: zad pa med de bsdus la thong rjes bkra ri
NK036(chi)026:291: rdol ba kun gyi thugs la gsal //
NK036(chi)026:292: 'on kyang bstan gtso sgrol ma thugs dad na spro phyir ka ba can du 'khor ba dong sprugs /
NK036(chi)026:294: ka ba can du kun bzang yab yum dang /
NK036(chi)026:295: o rgyan dam pa dbu rje ba /
NK036(chi)026:305: zhig mo rang grol rnams mthong /
NK036(chi)026:307: lhan skyes rta mgrin mkha' 'gro bla ma bcu gsum rnams //
NK036(chi)026:308: gsal dag 'ja' 'od dkyil na dngos su bzhugs pa mthong //
NK036(chi)026:309: mos gus gdung ba'i yid kyis gsol ba btab pa'i tshe //
NK036(chi)026:310: e ma nam mkha' nas gsungs /
NK036(chi)026:311: blo bral sems kyi gnas lugs brjod gzhi bral //
NK036(chi)026:312: lta sgom spyod 'bras med par sems thag chod //
NK036(chi)026:313: skal ldan snying po rtogs pas rgyal ba'i sras //
NK036(chi)026:314: tshul chos 'dzin pa thongs shig rnal 'byor pa //
NK036(chi)026:315: zhes gsungs mi snang nam mkha'i dbyings su yal nas thal //
NK036(chi)026:316: bla ma'i bzhugs nas seng+ge rgyab /
NK036(chi)026:317: dung lung nyid du bsdad pa'i tshe //
NK036(chi)026:318: yid 'ong bu mo gzhon pa'i gsung dbyangs snyan po yis //
NK036(chi)026:319: gzugs med +aahmh'u sgra yis bar snang khams rnams gang //
NK036(chi)026:321: yang dus tshes chos rdzong du /
NK036(chi)026:322: bcu gcig gi tho rangs sgra gcig grags /
NK036(chi)026:323: gnyid sad mkha' la bltas tshe mkha' 'gro sde bzhi yis //
NK036(chi)026:324: mgrin gcig bsdebs te snyan pa'i gsung dbyangs 'di ltar thos //
NK036(chi)026:325: e ma blo bde'i mal du chos nyid don bltas pas //
NK036(chi)026:329: bsgrub rim srog 'phrog mkha' 'gro'i snying po 'bru lnga'i rgyun bzlas pas //
NK036(chi)026:331: med stong grogs bya yis snying gi bu //
NK036(chi)026:335: yang nyin phyed yol tsam na gnyid du song ba'i
NK036(chi)026:336: rmi lam du mthong bas lus sbrid la gnyid sad
NK036(chi)026:338: cig ka ba can du tshes grangs bcu gnyis la //
NK036(chi)026:339: phag mo zhal dngos su mthong /
NK036(chi)026:342: gnyis med nam mkha'i dkyil du 'od du 'bar ba mthong //
NK036(chi)026:343: zhen med mchog gi dngos grub sprang po nyid kyis thob //
NK036(chi)026:344: bla ma'i sangs rgyas ras pa /
NK036(chi)026:345: gshegs shul dar chung nyid du bsdad pa'i tshe //
NK036(chi)026:346: rmi lam tshes bcu gsum gyi nub mo /
NK036(chi)026:347: phag mo 'khor bcas snying po 'bru lnga /
NK036(chi)026:349: de dus sa g.yos gnyid sad dmar po phub tsam pa'i dkyil du 'od khru gang pa gcig byung /
NK036(chi)026:352: sras po 'ja' rang gi bu chung skyes pa'i dus /
NK036(chi)026:353: tshon ring bsrel sgra ru bcas //
NK036(chi)026:354: gnas sprang po mchog dpal gyi skyabs gnas rdzong du bsdad pa'i tshe //
NK036(chi)026:355: bla ma rnam bla ma sku gshegs za lung pa /
NK036(chi)026:359: lnga mkha' 'gro rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK036(chi)026:360: tshes bco lnga'i nub mo mkha' 'gro sde lnga rdo rjee sems dpa' /
NK036(chi)026:362: chen dkyil 'khor zhal phye bum dbang gsang dbang shes
NK036(chi)026:363: rab ye shes dbang tshig dbang rin po che bzhi
NK036(chi)026:364: pa'i dbang ngo // bzhi rdzogs dbang //
NK036(chi)026:365: brda don zab mos ngo sprad rigs lnga yab yum mthong //
NK036(chi)026:366: bar chad rkyen rnams mang yang rtags bsdad du ma
NK036(chi)026:367: byung yang bar chad mang bas rig pa 'ur te
NK036(chi)026:368: thon rjes phur pa chu brag me la brtul zhugs
NK036(chi)026:371: gdams pa'i gnad yod rjes 'jug ya dod yod rnams /
NK036(chi)026:373: rtsa drug lon tshe sh+aan+t+ai ba'i dbang bzhi rdzogs pa /
NK036(chi)026:374: ri khrod 'khrul mthu snom ma bu tshogs drug la sogs pa zhig dar ma la /
NK036(chi)026:375: gsang sngags thabs lam gnad zhus ci byas chos su btang //
NK036(chi)026:376: tshe 'dir mi kha za skur pa /
NK036(chi)026:377: yang rang nyid don dang ldan //
NK036(chi)026:378: sprul sku rgya mtsho'i mtshan can chos kyi 'brel ba'i bla ma /
NK036(chi)026:380: theg chen snying po'i don gsung dug rnams zas su gyur //
NK036(chi)026:382: dbang phyug phag chos rje 'brug pa'i gdams ngag sna rdo rje gdan pa dang //
NK036(chi)026:383: mkhas btsun grub thob brten nas gdams ngag dpag med zhus //
NK036(chi)026:384: lar ni mtshan nyid ldan pa'i bla ma bcu gsum bsten //
NK036(chi)026:385: 'gran zla rtsod pa bral ba'i bla ma rnam gsum lags //
NK036(chi)026:389: khyad 'phags rdzogs chen 'di las lhag pa med /
NK036(chi)026:390: dran mchog bla ma gu ru la //
NK036(chi)026:391: gsang ba snying tig rgyud rnams pha pad gnyis kyis zhus //
NK036(chi)026:392: da lta sum cu lon nas ma shi'i bar du yang //
NK036(chi)026:393: 'jig rten sgyu ma'i nor la zhen pa spu tsam med //
NK036(chi)026:394: smyon 'di mi byed bya ba med pa /
NK036(chi)026:395: spyod byis pa'i rnam thar ngo tsha sba gsang bral //
NK036(chi)026:397: lha sku zhal mang po mthong /
NK036(chi)026:398: 'bum phrag zhal zhi khro'i lha tshogs /
NK036(chi)026:401: khros ma'i snying rlung zhugs pas gzhan 'ur 'grogs /
NK036(chi)026:402: dbang khong na zhe bcad yod pas /
NK036(chi)026:404: byin rlabs nyams rmi lam tsam sgyu ma tsam brag dang chu dang me dang mtshon /
NK036(chi)026:405: myong 'ur na thams cad rdzun po yin //
NK036(chi)026:406: 'di yin zla ba mun sel nam 'chi mi rtag bden pa med do don rang ngo bos stong //
NK036(chi)026:409: med byin brlabs 'byung gi rjes 'jug don gnyis bsgrub la rem //
NK036(chi)026:411: bslus pa med gdams ngag zab chos bshad /
NK036(chi)026:412: do bsam mno legs par thongs gtan du mi 'grogs /
NK036(chi)026:414: g.yar po yin pas 'byung ba bzhi la gtod //
NK036(chi)026:416: chos rang byas pas dpa' bo mkha' 'gros bsu //
NK036(chi)026:417: bla ma rang rig sems su byon pas dbyings gnyis gcig yin chu la chu thim /
NK036(chi)026:420: dang sgra dang rtags rnams ma sku gdung 'bar ba las bshad pa bzhin /
NK036(chi)026:425: par gyur pa'i yin chos 'adibadena pa'i tan blor mi shongs //
NK036(chi)026:428: ma lus kun bzang klong du nye bar 'gyur //
NK036(chi)026:429: 'di bris dge bas 'gro drug ma lus pa //
NK036(chi)026:430: rnam dag ye shes klong du sgyu lus dag gyur nas //
NK036(chi)026:431: gnyis med chos mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin skyes te bde ba chen po la 'khod do //
NK036(chi)026:432: kyi dbyings su mya ngan 'da' gyur cig /
NK036(chi)026:433: me long rdo rje'i rnam thar gsal byed rdzun gyi me long zhes bya ba /
NK036(chi)026:434: dad gus can gyi dbon kun gyis yang yang bskul nas /
NK036(chi)026:435: bya lo zla ba dang po'i tshes bco lnga la tshar bar bris pa lags so //
NK036(chi)026:436: ma ni pad+me h'u h+r+aih +aahmh'u h+r+aih 'bar kha'i mi kha bsdus kyang e ma g.yas re chung /
NK036(chi)026:438: bla ma dam pa des 'das rjes gsungs pa /
NK036(chi)026:439: nga 'gro skye med chos kyi dbyings su 'gro //
NK036(chi)026:440: rdzogs chen rnal 'byor dud yal nam mkha' 'dra //
NK036(chi)026:441: stong nyid sad chen 'khrul rtog sprin tshogs gtor //
NK036(chi)026:442: chos sku'i snang ba yin no e ma ho //
NK036(chi)026:443: snying tig rnal 'byor bar snang 'ja' tshon 'dra //
NK036(chi)026:444: rang rig shel sgong khri gdugs 'od dang mjal //
NK036(chi)026:445: longs sku'i snang ba yin no e ma ho //
NK036(chi)026:446: rgya grol rnal 'byor nam langs nyi shar 'dra //
NK036(chi)026:447: 'khor 'das kun khyab gang mos der snang ston //
NK036(chi)026:448: sprul sku'i snang ba yin no e ma ho //
NK036(chi)026:449: ngo bo stong pa'i dbyings ni bsam brjod bral //
NK036(chi)026:450: de la nga thim dge bas phan ma btags //
NK036(chi)026:451: rang bzhin 'od lnga'i dbyings ni zhi khror gsal //
NK036(chi)026:452: de nyid nga yin sdig pas gnod ma bskyal //
NK036(chi)026:453: thugs rje 'gag med dbyings ni sna tshogs ldan //
NK036(chi)026:454: de la ngas khyab 'bral med sku gsung ngang //
NK036(chi)026:455: sprang po ye shes lus su gyur pa la //
NK036(chi)026:456: med snyam ma sems 'bral med nyag gcig ltos //
NK036(chi)026:457: don med rags sku ma byed sgrub la 'bungs //
NK036(chi)026:458: gang 'byor bla ma'i gsung yin phyogs med mchod //
NK036(chi)026:459: skyon rtogs 'thab rtsod ma byed khyi phyugs spongs //
NK036(chi)026:460: ngas bshad gdams pa nyams longs gsol ba thob //
NK036(chi)026:461: chags sdang rjes chod thig le nyag gcig ltos //
NK036(chi)026:462: zhen med rnam thar yin no lad mo zlos //
NK036(chi)026:463: ri khrod pha yul yin no bya ba thong //
NK036(chi)026:464: de ltar byas na skyid 'byung mngon sangs rgyas //
NK036(chi)026:465: zhes phyi rabs kyi don du snang bar byas so //
